{"tid":693150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警拒7.1遊行崇光起步","createTime":"2018-06-07T08:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T10:45:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"091234ef7852c2e55275f2a9e4bb8fb6caff8b8d","tid":693150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413358&d=7IROXZj%2B%2BNRNlnucVjSBmW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=8d1e3587\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180607%2F20413358&h=26ffa2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180607/20413358</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月07日 <br />\n<br />\n警拒7.1遊行崇光起步<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180607/large/a0902a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180607%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.gif&h=c883e736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年7.1遊行於維園起步，參加者被警方鐵馬陣阻隔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民間人權陣線原計劃今年7.1遊行於維園起步，再次被親中團體搶先申請，需由維園草地出發。民陣表明反對，改向警方申請於銅鑼灣東角道或軒尼詩道與渣甸街交界起步，惟警方以人流管制問題對建議有保留，本月中才決定是否發出不反對通知書。民陣副召集人、立法會議員區諾軒批評，警方拒絕接納民陣提出的多項建議，「係一個好離譜情況」。<br />\n<br />\n維園硬地足球場被搶閘申請，民陣計劃改於銅鑼灣東角道作為7.1遊行起步點，或於軒尼詩道與渣甸街交界集合，即崇光百貨對面，預計有3,000人，早前已向警方申請不反對通知書，昨午雙方會面逾一小時，但建議暫未被警方接納，認為東角道不適合集會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只准選維園草地<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人葉志衍表示，在會上多次向警方強調，民陣會增派糾察及做好街站呼籲。但警方有保留，指東角道地方太小，無法容納太多人；渣甸街則有暗斜，不宜集會，又恐引起港鐵站人流倒灌，甚至建議民陣呼籲團體於中環才設街站，並重申只有維園草地可選擇，不作其他建議。<br />\n<br />\n他說，料本月中警方才決定是否發出不反對通知書，民陣會再研究銅鑼灣有否合適地點作遊行起步，否則很大機會在東角道出發。他期望7.1遊行能順利舉行，「對香港市民係一個好好表達聲音嘅權利」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n政府研電子點票公僕先投　冀2020立會選舉推行<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n梁耀忠：非避叫結束一黨專政"},{"pid":"155522c88f5597c39324159bf68c43f14aab0494","tid":693150,"uid":25002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86b2c2aa5e79dcd7115f200e18527db2cdd91375","tid":693150,"uid":9726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6362a7a5508cdcfd84272f52626519e89769ba43","tid":693150,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534ec609004fd7e449e21511363485edfb566462","tid":693150,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"邊到放多街站錢箱, 咪邊到起步囉<br />\n<br />\nD錢箱流動架嘛<br />\n<br />\n是撚旦啦"},{"pid":"67ec101f83613ae6fc82cbde8778b60e86eac4ed","tid":693150,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86b2c2aa5e79dcd7115f200e18527db2cdd91375","tid":693150,"uid":9726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"有行人專用區, <br />\n<br />\n放到多街站錢箱"},{"pid":"ff69dc226d58142ec1979a5abbc9c74517ed478c","tid":693150,"uid":74058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"534ec609004fd7e449e21511363485edfb566462","tid":693150,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"邊到放多街站錢箱, 咪邊到起步囉<br />\n<br />\nD錢箱流動架嘛<br />\n<br />\n是撚旦啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"學聯個錢箱係移動咪得"},{"pid":"518088263b21f002796a970b52bd77c1f107ac28","tid":693150,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T09:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />